title: Seventies
alt: Hey, man, the 1670s called. They were like 'Wherefore this demonic inſtrument? By what ſorcery does it produce ſuch ſounds?"
transcript:
Cueball: Nice jacket. Hey–
Cueball: The seventies called.
Out-of-panel: Oh? What'd they want?[Cueball looks at his smartphone, holding it in his hand.]
Cueball: I don't know. They didn't leave a message.
Out-of-panel: Weird.1974:
[A person in bell bottoms looks at a rotary phone receiver, who has no jacket.]
Voicemail service: If you'd like to leave a message, press "1".
